  <name>MyApps</name>
  <summary>View and manage installed Linux applications</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="de">Installierte Linux-Anwendungen anzeigen und verwalten</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      MyApps is a user-friendly tool for Linux that displays all installed applications
      clearly - without system clutter.
    </p>
    <p xml:lang="de">
      MyApps ist ein benutzerfreundliches Tool für Linux, das alle installierten
      Anwendungen übersichtlich darstellt - ohne System-Clutter.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-distribution support (Debian, Ubuntu, Mint, Arch, Fedora, etc.)</li>
      <li>Modern GTK4 + Libadwaita GUI with native dark mode</li>
      <li>Virtual scrolling for 10,000+ packages without performance issues</li>
      <li>Intelligent filtering of system apps</li>
      <li>Icons with system integration</li>
      <li>Search function (name + description)</li>
      <li>Export functions (TXT, CSV, JSON)</li>
      <li>Multilingual (German, English)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

